{"tid":2368247,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國組織「香港民主委員會」 ：有年輕人乘船逃離香港後抵美國尋庇護","createTime":"2021-01-16T04:33:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T11:25:52.000Z","uid":20933,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8e7e443f6382c66cd53d199b31d8040d8278c416","tid":2368247,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T04:33:31.000Z","msg":"美國組織「香港民主委員會」總監朱牧民發聲明，指一群30歲以下的香港抗爭者乘船逃離香港後抵達美國。聲明指，他們參加了香港仍在進行的民主抗爭活動，並面臨逮捕和指控，去年7月乘船逃離香港，有賴美國及其他支持者一直提供庇護和保護。組織會協助他們尋求庇護及展開新生活。 <br />\n<br />\n聲明又敦促美國政府，繼續制裁負責香港大規模逮捕和鎮壓行動的人士，並採取大膽行動，歡迎逃離政治迫害的抗爭人士和他們的直系親屬。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2375051\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2375051&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyL%2FjevXO%2BySp3REELKrGah4%3D&h=131cc6f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2375051</a>"},{"pid":"c7efc7f16356347ca83fb157a7116b7ec378d3b5","tid":2368247,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T04:41:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c8341ca61c42b5cb20d3bfbac28f04d1f55f670","tid":2368247,"uid":2676,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T04:42:27.000Z","msg":"搭船去美國咁撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b19a179f54ba06257a40e7afbdfd78ad7731b777","tid":2368247,"uid":88133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c8341ca61c42b5cb20d3bfbac28f04d1f55f670","tid":2368247,"uid":2676,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T04:42:27.000Z","msg":"搭船去美國咁撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T04:45:48.000Z","msg":"搭船要搭幾多個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eab7af7e04034cf37b230e74572173048d4b6402","tid":2368247,"uid":267494,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"9c83